  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a world inspired by nightmares, where every jump counts, and the smallest mistake can be fatal. <i>Hostile Dreams 2</i> is not just a game—it’s a mental challenge that constantly pushes your limits. With its unique ragdoll controls, unforgiving levels, and oppressive atmosphere, this experience will haunt you long after you stop playing.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What does the game offer?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique ragdoll controls</strong> – Thanks to physics-based mechanics, no two jumps will ever be the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rely on your survival instincts</strong> – There are no weapons, only you, your reflexes, and your decisions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Constant tension</strong> – Every move is a risk, and you never know what’s coming next.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The sweet taste of success</strong> – After suffering and failing, the joy of triumph makes it all worthwhile.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautifully oppressive world</strong> – Stunning yet deadly environments where beauty hides danger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test your mental limits</strong> – How long can you endure the tension and failure?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/088cb03bcb48aaeb368ffbf2be7c2d8f.webp?t=1744307822\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/ce573a655859e8921029031c40264568.poster.avif?t=1744307822\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/ce573a655859e8921029031c40264568.webm?t=1744307822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/ce573a655859e8921029031c40264568.mp4?t=1744307822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death is a common visitor in this world, but don't worry; in <strong>Normal</strong> mode, checkpoints offer a relative sense of safety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, <strong>Hostile</strong> mode is strictly for those who want to hurt themselves!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/088cb03bcb48aaeb368ffbf2be7c2d8f.webp?t=1744307822\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/4eca4d9402ea6f202b5c834a46aec4b6.poster.avif?t=1744307822\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/4eca4d9402ea6f202b5c834a46aec4b6.webm?t=1744307822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/4eca4d9402ea6f202b5c834a46aec4b6.mp4?t=1744307822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The key to survival is patience, learning, and executing precise jumps!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Are you ready to face Hostile Dreams 2 and push beyond your limits?</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>*This game is not a direct sequel but the successor to the first one, so prior knowledge of it is not required.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/088cb03bcb48aaeb368ffbf2be7c2d8f.webp?t=1744307822\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p>",
